data.description: This meticulously upgraded 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence,948 living space, stands as the paragon of sophisticated elegance. Originally constructed in 1953, this home has undergone a comprehensive remodel since 2023, featuring all-new exterior and interior paint.  Step into a luminous and inviting interior that seamlessly blends classic charm with contemporary flair. The home is a testament to energy efficiency with solar, incorporating sustainable design elements that not only reduce environmental impact but also contribute to substantial cost savings.  The three generously sized bedrooms and two impeccably designed bathrooms exude luxury and comfort. The kitchen, the heart of this home, showcases high-end appliances and nice finishes, making it a haven for culinary enthusiasts. Strategically located in San Bernardino, this property provides easy access to amenities, schools, and recreational hubs. Priced competitively, this fully upgraded residence is the epitome of value and sophistication. Secure your chance to own this exciting blend of timeless elegance and cutting-edge design! Professional Pictures coming soon
